Rêve Collection R70233 Toyota Starlet 1973 Fuji Test

As mentioned here, the Toyota Starlet made it’s debut in Round 5 of the 1973 Minor Touring Series. The model seen here represents the car as it looked in its first real-life test conducted on October 25, 1973 at Fuji Speedway about 1 month prior to it's debut race.
